The paper deals with object co-segmentation using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed attention mechanism and algorithm for linear time complexity involve machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of multiple datasets and experiment results suggest a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) applications.
